## ğŸš€ Overview

This project showcases an interactive **Sales Performance Dashboard** built using Tableau. The dashboard enables business stakeholders to monitor key sales metrics, analyze regional trends, and identify high-performing product categories to drive data-driven decisions.

ğŸ‘‰ **Live Dashboard:** [View on Tableau Public](https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/abhijith.thakur/viz/SalesDashboard)

